{
  "stem": "22869.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't realize that-- that they already know that I'm not here anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he took my bread, and he never went to notify them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, these blocks were not any further away than here houses are from each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So next day, I begged him and I cajoled him again, and again, and again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in the evening, he finally took away again my ration-- or the additive that was with the ration, maybe a piece of horse salami or whatever they gave you, and he went and he notified them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember like today when my two brothers came to the window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like they looked at somebody who just got up from the dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they started crying and begging and saying, get out of here!",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Get out of here!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I says, I feel a little better now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm going to tell them, and I'm going to try to get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And sure enough, the next day, I really, you know, picked up a little strength.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was feeling a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was like a-- like a miracle that this guy takes my pulse, and he says, I think he has typhus, and he sends me back to the-- to the-- to the-- it was like an angel showed up there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, if I think back today, it's like-- it's like a guardian angel showing up and says, you go back inside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If I would have stayed outside, I would really been gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the next day, I told the guy that I feel much better, and they let me go out there again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then I joined my brothers again in the detail, at which time they came to camp with-- some SS guy came to camp with a civilian guy.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
